ST MARGARETS TRADERS ASSOCIATION'S ADAM TOCOCK STEPS DOWN
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    After many years of service, Adam Tocock is stepping down from his
    role with the St Margarets Traders Association. Adam helped
    organise the group and all their activities, including publishing
    the wonderful St Margarets magazines and running the semi-annual
    Crown Road fairs. It is hard and often unappreciated work, but Adam
    pushed forward with a smile on his face and a ready joke. Thank you
    Adam and we will see you at Cutters.

