MOORMEAD FC BIDS TO SAVE THE MOORMEAD PARK PAVILLION
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    On Saturday 16 January 2016, hundreds of St Margarets residents
    braved freezing temperatures to show their support for the
    renovation of Moormead Park Pavilion.

    Parents from Moormead Football Club are waiting to hear back
    from Richmond Council about their community-led 'expression
    of interest' to restore the Pavilion building, which was submitted
    in December last year.

